	In: Birch, H et al. (2021): Raw Data for article Ecosystem Function after the K/Pg Extinction: Decoupling of Marine Carbon Pump and Diversity [dataset bundled publication]. PANGAEA, https://doi.org/10.1594/PANGAEA.935502
Abstract:	Core samples were washed over a 38µm sieve and dried in an oven at 40°C. Planktic foraminifera species and genera abundance counts were made on 49 samples.
